{"tid":731204,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學嗰陣 有冇遇過黑箱作業嘅經歷？","createTime":"2018-07-06T04:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T13:37:28.000Z","uid":137840,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0175556518c40f846e6cda04b04f4c6e98b976","tid":731204,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"好耐之前 果時讀緊中學<br />\n有年音樂比賽 有個參賽者A同 其中一位評判老師非常熟<br />\n果時我負責計分<br />\n之後嗰位評判老師俾佢好高分 超出其餘兩三位評判十幾廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大出入<br />\n但係佢比其他人嘅分數 好低 徘徊喺50-60 分，但係同學A 80幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後果位A同學攞咗冠軍<br />\n依家諗返起都覺得 中學已經黑哨 幾咁可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a8b3b99c7d48e0fc5e2a75bc8e3c08b2e496ec","tid":731204,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"有冇開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c95014d8774758bbc2f984360c8cefd51f3b78","tid":731204,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打有經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a290d9e0895abfd9eb36e4e4a90d7673deb4a1d","tid":731204,"uid":12597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"學生會 得一個閣 唔夠一半票嗰年就會冇學生會，冇曬活動<br />\n有年個閣太垃圾，唔夠票 學校照做到佢哋當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3037910d91096fff8165b7c4fd43790d7963ee4","tid":731204,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a290d9e0895abfd9eb36e4e4a90d7673deb4a1d","tid":731204,"uid":12597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"學生會 得一個閣 唔夠一半票嗰年就會冇學生會，冇曬活動<br />\n有年個閣太垃圾，唔夠票 學校照做到佢哋當選<img src=\"/assets/f